title: Hamburger menu (upper left corner) consist of TO-DO list and Statistic sections
preconditions: 1. The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on Tablet LENOVO TB-7304L
steps_actions:
1. Open the application "TO-DO-MVP"
2. Tap on Hamburger menu (upper left corner)
steps_result:
1. The initial screen of application is opened
2. The TO_DO list and Statistics sections are appeared

title: Hamburger menu: Tapping on Statistic button opens statistic with active and completed tasks
preconditions:
1.The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on real device Lenovo TB-7304l
2\. Some tasks were created
steps_actions:
1. Tap on Hamburger menu (upper left corner)
2. Tap on Statistics
steps_result:
1. The TO_DO list and Statistics sections are appeared
2. Statistic screen with information about active and completed tasks appears

title: Hamburger menu: Tapping on TO_DO List a general list of tasks is displayed (All TO-DOs)
preconditions:
1.The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on real device Lenovo TB-7304l
2\. Some task were created
steps_actions:
1. Tap on Hamburger menu (upper left corner)
2. Tap on TO_DO List
steps_result:
1. The TO_DO list and Statistics sections are appeared
2. A general list of tasks is displayed (All TO-DOs)

title: Creating a new task: Numbers in the Title
preconditions:
1. The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on Tablet LENOVO TB-7304L
2. The app's initial screen is open
steps_actions:
1. Tap on the "+" button in the lower right corner
2. Fill in the Title with Numbers
3. Tap the ✓ (lower right corner) button in the list
steps_result:
1. The New TO-DO screen opens
2. The entered data appears in the Title
3. The task with the entered Title has been created

title: Statistic section: returning to the initial screen by swiping the screen from left to right or by pressing the ← button.
preconditions:
1.The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on real device Lenovo TB-7304l
2\. The initial screen opened
steps_actions:
1. Tap on Hamburger menu (upper left corner)
2. Tap on Statistics
3. Swipe rom the left side of the screen to the right or tap the "←" button
steps_result:
1. The TO_DO list and Statistics sections are appeared
2. Statistic screen with information about active and completed tasks appears
3. Returns to the initial screen

title: TO-Do List/ All To-DOs: checking the ability of edit Title or Description
preconditions:
1.The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on real device Lenovo TB-7304l
2\. The task " New Year celebration" was created
steps_actions:
1. Tap on Hamburger menu (upper left corner)
2. Tap on TO_DO List
3. Mark check-box "New Year celebration" task
4. Tap on edit button ( [![Edit this at Wikidata](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/8a/OOjs_UI_icon_edit-ltr-progressive.svg/10px-OOjs_UI_icon_edit-ltr-progressive.svg.png)](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q1046333#P856 "Edit this at Wikidata")) in the lower right corner
5. Edit Title or Description
6. Tap on the "✓ "(lower right corner) button
steps_result:
1. The TO_DO list and Statistics sections are appeared
2. A general list of tasks is displayed (All TO-DOs)
3. The checkbox is marked in the task "New Year celebration" task
4. The ability of edit task appears
5. The symbols appear in Title or Description fields
6. The task is resaved with changes

title: Creating a new task: creating multiple tasks with the same Title is prohibited.
preconditions:
1.The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on real device Lenovo TB-7304l
2\. The task " New Year celebration" was created
steps_actions:
1. Tap TO_DO list from Hamburger menu (upper left corner)
2. Tap on the "+" button in the lower right corner
3. Fill in the Title with an existing title
steps_result:
1. A general list of tasks is displayed (All TO-DOs)
2. The New TO-DO screen opens
3. The message "A task with this Title exists. Change Title" appears.

title: Creating a new task: Cancel creating a new task and return to the initial page via "←" button
preconditions:
1. The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on Tablet LENOVO TB-7304L
2. The app's initial screen is open
steps_actions:

2. Tap "←" button
steps_result:
1. The New TO-DO screen opens
2. Returns to the previous screen. New task not created

title: Kebab menu / "Refresh" button  refreshes the screen with saving all app's information
preconditions:
1.The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on real device Lenovo TB-7304l
2\. Some tasks were created
steps_actions:
1. Open All TO-DOs list
2. Tap the Kebab menu (upper right corner)
3. Tap the "Refresh" button
steps_result:
1. List with existing tasks is open
2. The "Clear completed" and "Refresh" section appear
3. The screen is updated. All information is saved

title: Kebab menu / "Clear completed" button clears the list of completed tasks
preconditions:
1.The application "TO-DO-MVP is installed and opened on real device Lenovo TB-7304l
2\. Some tasks were created
steps_actions:
1. Open All TO-DOs list
2. Tick task
3. Tap the Kebab menu (upper right corner)
4. Tap the "Clear completed" button
steps_result:
1. List with existing tasks is open
2. Task marked check-box. Pop-up message "Task is completed" appears
3. The "Clear completed" and "Refresh" section appear
4. The list of completed task is cleared
